item.title: Hello World!!!
item.description: It has been a loooong time since I’ve blogged. Like, almost 7 years since I posted anything on my personal blog. The thing is: I really didn’t have much to say. I have been heads-down at Khan Academy doing all sorts of awesome things. In that time, I became a Staff Engineer, contributed significantly to our massive re-write, and even became a manager! Something that is interesting me these days that I feel like I want to talk about: AI Generated code.
